cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CE 

The paper proposes a machine learning approach that uses deep networks to estimate AF recurrence by predicting shape descriptors directly from MRI images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The use of deep networks also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the proposed data augmentation scheme involves generating new data, which could be relevant to the computer engineering (cs.CE) category.
